
  Altaria    Dragon Type Pokémon

  ALTARIA dances and wheels through 
  the sky among billowing, cotton-like 
  clouds.  By singing melodies 
  in its crystal-clear voice, this 
  Pokémon makes its listeners experience 
  dreamy wonderment. 
	Evolution Chain
      Swablu ► Altaria

